-- Fewer Danish Borrowers in Arrears in 1Q, Mortgage Group Says
-- B y   F r a n c e s   S c h w a r t z k o p f f
-- 2013-05-01T07:14:23Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-05-01/fewer-danish-borrowers-in-arrears-in-1q-mortgage-group-says.html
The number of homeowners who are in
arrears on their mortgage payments fell in the first quarter by
150 to about 4,400, the Association of Danish Mortgage Banks
says in an e-mailed statement.
*Says number of homeowners behind on payments have fallen by
half in the past three years
*Shows borrowers’ financial state “generally is robust,” Ane
Arnth Jensen, association’s director, says  To contact the reporter on this story:
